==發行==
===評價===
《少年彌賽亞》獲得了褒貶不一的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據32篇專業影評，評級50%，平均得分5.7／10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_young_messiah/ |title=The Young Messiah (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=March 18, 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325033454/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_young_messiah/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分33，評價偏差<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-young-messiah |title=The Young Messiah reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=March 14, 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323044913/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-young-messiah |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[影院評分|影院評分]]調查，觀眾從A+至F之間平均給了「A-」的評價<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/10-cloverfield-lane-brothers-grimsby-zootopia-weekend-box-office-1201718537/ |title=Audiences Booking Trips To ‘Zootopia’ & ’10 Cloverfield Lane’ |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-03-22 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613084548/https://deadline.com/2016/03/10-cloverfield-lane-brothers-grimsby-zootopia-weekend-box-office-1201718537/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
在美國和加拿大，該片於2016年3月11日和《[[科洛弗10號地窖|科洛弗10號地窖]]》、《[[特務大臨演|特務大臨演]]》和《{{link-en|完美的一對|The Perfect Match (2016 film)}}》共同上映。初步預估首映當天能獲得700至800萬美元的票房，但實際上映後卻只獲得了140萬美元<ref name="#1"/>。首週末票房為330萬美元<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/10-cloverfield-lane-brothers-grimsby-zootopia-box-office-preview-1201716865/ |title=‘Zootopia’ Turnstiles Still Spinning, But ‘10 Cloverfield Lane’ Also A Hot Destination – Box Office Preview |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-03-22 |archive-date=2016-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323145611/http://deadline.com/2016/03/10-cloverfield-lane-brothers-grimsby-zootopia-box-office-preview-1201716865/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

